{"data":[{"date":"07:19 06/07","title":"Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Brazil ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ebft World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/tru-cot-danilo-chan-thuong-nghi-het-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t th\u00fa v\u1ecb khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 phong c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 nhau. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu \u0111i v\u00e0o chi ti\u1ebft, s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o World Cup 2018, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. T\u1edbi gi\u1edd ph\u00fat n\u00e0y, Les Bleus \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y qua tr\u1eadn kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Didier Deschamps d\u1eabn d\u1eaft ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1p l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e2n t\u00e0i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. B\u1ed9 ba Griezmann, Giroud v\u00e0 Mbappe ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t \u0103n \u00fd v\u00e0 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 h\u01a1n. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Uruguay, \u0111\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 2-1 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p (21h ng\u00e0y 67) t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p (21h ng\u00e0y 67) t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Nhan-dinh-Uruguay-vs-Phap-(21h-ngay-67)-tu-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p 21h ng\u00e0y 6/7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p, kh\u00f4ng ai d\u00e1m xem th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9. T\u00ednh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Diego Godin c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Sau 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi duy nh\u1ea5t 1 b\u00e0n t\u1eeb t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng Uruguay v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a g\u1eb7p thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m. B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 m\u00ecnh Cristiano Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u0169i c\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn La Celeste g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Ai C\u1eadp, Saudi Arabia r\u1ed3i Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cavani ghi ban cho Uruguay truoc Nga\" title=\"Cavani ghi ban cho Uruguay truoc Nga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/HLV-Tabarez-phat-bieu-sau-tran-Uruguay-3-0-Nga-day-nuoi-tiec-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Uruguay ch\u01b0a g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1p s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u0169i c\u00f4ng, nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng. Tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 l\u1ee5c l\u0103ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Fekir, Dembele, Thauvin hay Lemar \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 t\u00e0i v\u00e0 m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi Kante c\u00e0n qu\u00e9t \u1edf ph\u00eda sau, Ph\u00e1p c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i c\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Pogba m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 l\u00e0 c\u00f3 15 l\u00e1 ph\u1ed5i lu\u00f4n thu\u1ed9c t\u1ed1p nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00ecnh tham d\u1ef1. Ch\u00ednh Kante \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n h\u1ed3i sinh Pogba sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u01b0a nh\u01b0 \u00fd t\u1ea1i Man United.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o gu\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 n\u1eefa l\u00e0 Uruguay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 (sau Peru v\u00e0 Argentina).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-thang-tien-tu-ket-world-cup-cong-thuc-chien-thang-mang-ten-pogbappe-421-190444.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/phap-thang-tien-tu-ket-world-cup-cong-thuc-chien-thang-mang-ten-pogbappe.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-thang-tien-tu-ket-world-cup-cong-thuc-chien-thang-mang-ten-pogbappe-421-190444.html\">Ph\u00e1p th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup: C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng mang t\u00ean Pogbappe</span><br>\r\n<span>Kazan, 30 th\u00e1ng S\u00e1u 2018, Ph\u00e1p 4-3 Argentina. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 chia tay World Cup, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00e3i m\u00e3i, \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i cho...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nUruguay thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, Uruguay s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111i t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qu\u00ean nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Luis Suarez v\u00e0 Edinson Cavani.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00e0y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi mang t\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Uruguay. C\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb b\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1ee3c khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Tabarez d\u1eabn d\u1eaft thi\u1ebfu \u0111i Cavani.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cavani chan thuong nghi tran vs Phap\" title=\"Cavani chan thuong nghi tran vs Phap\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Cavani-chan-thuong-nghi-tran-vs-Phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Cavani ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha khi\u1ebfn Cavani kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u0169ng c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Uruguay b\u1edfi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf PSG \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Suarez \u1edf th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Uruguay. Hu\u1ed1ng chi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u World Cup 2018 t\u1edbi nay, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 31 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ed9 r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi sau khi c\u00e0y \u1ea3i c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a c\u00f9ng Barcelona. Chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a La Celeste ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"griezmann va Suarez\" title=\"griezmann va Suarez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/griezmann-va-Suarez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ch\u1ec9 Suarez kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng so \u0111\u1ecd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao Ph\u00e1p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Uruguay. Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean ti\u1ec1n tuy\u1ebfn v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 th\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u HLV Tabarez mong mu\u1ed1n. Song c\u0169ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho Cavani.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu gi\u1eef v\u1eefng 2 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u00ean, Tabarez s\u1ebd c\u00f3 2 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t gi\u00e0, m\u1ed9t tr\u1ebb l\u00e0 Cristhian Stuani v\u00e0 Maxi Gomez. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Stuani (31 tu\u1ed5i) ch\u1ec9 ghi 5 b\u00e0n sau 40 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Uruguay. C\u00f2n Gomez (21 tu\u1ed5i) m\u1edbi c\u00f3 6 tr\u1eadn qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/rami-tho-phao-khi-sat-thu-cavani-chan-thuong-nang-469-190410.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/rami-tho-phao-khi-sat-thu-cavani-chan-thuong-nang.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/rami-tho-phao-khi-sat-thu-cavani-chan-thuong-nang-469-190410.html\">Trung v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p th\u1edf ph\u00e0o khi s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 Cavani ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng</span><br>\r\n<span>Trung v\u1ec7 Adil Rami \u0111\u00e3 th\u1edf ph\u00e0o nh\u1eb9 nh\u00f5m khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cavani d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong 8 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018, ch\u1ec9 Nga (21) l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra \u00edt c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Uruguay (25). Khi v\u1eafng &ldquo;tr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o&rdquo; Cavani, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i th\u1eddi c\u01a1 c\u1ee7a La Celeste c\u00e0ng b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Nizhny Novgorod 21h t\u1ed1i nay (6/7): Uruguay co c\u1ee5m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u1eb1m c\u1ea7u h\u00f2a Ph\u00e1p. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc l\u00f3e s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Les Bleus s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\nUruguay (4-3-2-1):</strong> 1.Muslera - 22.C\u00e1ceres, 2.Gim\u00e9nez, 3.God\u00edn, 17.Laxalt - 8.N\u00e1ndez, 14.Torreira, 15.Vecino - 6.Bentancur, 10.Arrascaeta - 9.Su\u00e1rez<br>\r\n<strong>Ph\u00e1p (4-2-3-1): </strong>1.Lloris - 2.Pavard, 4.Varane, 5.Umtiti, 21.Hern\u00e1ndez - 13.Kant\u00e9, 6.Pogba - 10.Mbapp\u00e9, 7.Griezmann, 18.Fekir - 9.Giroud<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: </strong>Ph\u00e1p th\u1eafng 1-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Uruguay vs Phap\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Uruguay-vs-Phap-(4-3-2-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/antoine-griezmann-phu-phang-voi-diego-godin-421-190167.html\">Antoine Griezmann ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng v\u1edbi Diego Godin</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ldbd-uruguay-xac-nhan-kha-nang-ra-san-cua-cavani-o-tran-gap-dt-phap-421-190362.html\">L\u0110B\u0110 Uruguay c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cavani tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/da-bai-bo-dao-nha-hlv-uruguay-no-tung-bung-469-190071.html\">\u0110\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, HLV Uruguay n\u1ed5 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/matuidi-khang-dinh-mbappe-se-toa-sang-hon-nua-469-190408.html\">Matuidi tin Mbappe s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1eafn h\u1ea1 Uruguay \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/torreira-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-uruguay-vs-phap-421-190425.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"948","checkdouble":"190464"},{"date":"07:40 06/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh l\u00e0m l\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/nguoi-dai-dien-vo-tinh-lam-lo-tuong-lai-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jorge Mendes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo. \u201cSi\u00eau c\u00f2\u201d n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng n\u00e0y v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin CR7 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus chi \u0111\u1eadm cho Ronaldo</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (100 tri\u1ec7u Euro) t\u1edbi Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 33, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Los Blancos th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qua 44 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 44 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n9 m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua t\u1ea1i Real, Ronaldo c\u0169ng lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu chinh ph\u1ee5c nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 4 Champions League v\u00e0 2 La Liga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mendes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mendes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/Mendes-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-Ronaldo-tai-Real-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00f3 tin Ronaldo chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n nh\u1edb ngay sau khi Real \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Liverpool \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League m\u00f9a 2017/18, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd, nghe \u0111\u00e2u c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Man United \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro/ m\u00f9a. Ch\u00ednh c\u1ef1u gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Luciano Moggi \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-juventus-180-190431.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus</span>.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mendes v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJorge Mendes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo trong l\u00fac d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn s\u1ee5c s\u00f4i. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao n\u00e0y g\u1ee3i \u00fd v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi. Qua \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec vi\u1ec7c Mendes x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Juventus trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jorge Mendes bi tinh nghi tron thue.\" title=\"Jorge Mendes b\u1ecb t\u00ecnh nghi tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/13/sau-cris-ronaldo-sieu-co-jorge-mendes-bi-dieu-tra-tron-thue.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mendes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea9n \u00fd</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;N\u1ebfu Cristiano Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd m\u00e3i m\u00e3i bi\u1ebft \u01a1n CLB, ng\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean y t\u1ebf, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c Madridistas tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi&rdquo;, Mendes n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u1edd Record. &ldquo;M\u1ed9t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n m\u1edbi v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi s\u1ebd m\u1edf ra trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Real t\u1eeb Man United n\u0103m 2009, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 450 b\u00e0n sau 438 tr\u1eadn cho h\u1ecd tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Anh \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1eafm gi\u1eef k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain-184-190405.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus s\u1edbm m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 song s\u00e1t t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo - Higuain</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/truyen-thong-chau-au-deu-khang-dinh-95-ronaldo-sang-juventus-180-190379.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 95% Ronaldo c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-24-de-che-siro-chua-the-sup-do-421-190218.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 24: \u0110\u1ebf ch\u1ebf &ldquo;Si-R\u00f4&rdquo; ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/an-tuong-world-cup/cristiano-ronaldo-cau-thu-co-tam-va-tai-471-190213.html\">B\u00e0i d\u1ef1 thi \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng World Cup: Cristiano Ronaldo - C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u00e2m v\u00e0 t\u00e0i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-va-messi-dat-tay-nhau-ve-nuoc-doan-ket-cuoc-hanh-trinh-421-190180.html\">Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi d\u1eaft tay nhau v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc: \u0110o\u1ea1n k\u1ebft cu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"947","checkdouble":"190465"},{"date":"07:56 06/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 6/7: Ronaldo g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juve","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-67-ronaldo-gan-nhu-la-nguoi-cua-juve.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 6/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Messi mu\u1ed1n Pogba t\u1edbi Barcelona.</strong> Lionel Messi mu\u1ed1n Barcelona k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba t\u1eeb Manchester United. Sau khi b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 Antoine Griezmann m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng ch\u00fa \u00fd sang m\u1ed9t tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p kh\u00e1c. Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Paulinho khu trung tuy\u1ebfn Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ronaldo g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juve. </strong>Theo th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Goal, Cristiano Ronaldo g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus. CR7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A v\u1ec1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro/ m\u00f9a. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 khi\u1ebfn cho ph\u00eda Real Madrid b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1edfi h\u1ecd mong ch\u1edd Ronaldo \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 67 Ronaldo g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juve h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 67 Ronaldo g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juve h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/Mendes-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-Ronaldo-tai-Real-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00f3 tin Ronaldo chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Argentina mu\u1ed1n thay Sampaoli. </strong>C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Mario Kempes mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV Argentina n\u1ebfu&nbsp; Jorge Sampaoli b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i. Sau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i, chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Sampaoli lung lay d\u1eef d\u1ed9i d\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2022.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i gia mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Shaqiri. </strong>Manchester United s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xherdan Shaqiri t\u1eeb Stoke City. Theo t\u1edd The Sun, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, ch\u00ednh c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Napoli m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho Jorginho t\u1edbi Man City. </strong>Napoli m\u1edbi c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Fabian Ruiz t\u1eeb Real Betis. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro. \u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Napoli coi nh\u01b0 m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho t\u1edbi Man City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Jorginho\" title=\"tien ve Jorginho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/26/man-city-sap-co-jorginho-cua-napoli.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Jorginho r\u1ed9ng c\u1eeda sang Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nBarca g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1edbi cho Willian.</strong> Barcelona \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1edbi cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Sau khi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m s\u1edf h\u1eefu tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Brazil th\u00f4ng qua con s\u1ed1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Tottenham v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Liverpol trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Grealish. </strong>Theo t\u1edd Mirror, Tottenham s\u1eafp gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool khi ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi anh.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nSouthgate v\u1eabn c\u1ea7m l\u00e1i Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2022.</strong> Ngay t\u1eeb b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n HLV Gareth Southgate. Theo th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Telegraph, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0a Tam s\u01b0 t\u1edbi VCK Euro 2020, Southgate s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng cho t\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 n\u0103m 2022.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"946","checkdouble":"190466"},{"date":"08:05 06/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p (21h ng\u00e0y 6/7): Th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 l\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng kh\u1ee7ng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/Nhan-dinh-Uruguay-vs-Phap-(21h-ngay-67)-tu-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t th\u00fa v\u1ecb khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 phong c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 nhau. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu \u0111i v\u00e0o chi ti\u1ebft, s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o World Cup 2018, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. T\u1edbi gi\u1edd ph\u00fat n\u00e0y, Les Bleus \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y qua tr\u1eadn kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Didier Deschamps d\u1eabn d\u1eaft ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1p l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e2n t\u00e0i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. B\u1ed9 ba Griezmann, Giroud v\u00e0 Mbappe ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t \u0103n \u00fd v\u00e0 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 h\u01a1n. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Uruguay, \u0111\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 2-1 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p (21h ng\u00e0y 67) t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p (21h ng\u00e0y 67) t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Nhan-dinh-Uruguay-vs-Phap-(21h-ngay-67)-tu-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p 21h ng\u00e0y 6/7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p, kh\u00f4ng ai d\u00e1m xem th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9. T\u00ednh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Diego Godin c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Sau 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi duy nh\u1ea5t 1 b\u00e0n t\u1eeb t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng Uruguay v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a g\u1eb7p thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m. B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 m\u00ecnh Cristiano Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u0169i c\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn La Celeste g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Ai C\u1eadp, Saudi Arabia r\u1ed3i Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cavani ghi ban cho Uruguay truoc Nga\" title=\"Cavani ghi ban cho Uruguay truoc Nga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/HLV-Tabarez-phat-bieu-sau-tran-Uruguay-3-0-Nga-day-nuoi-tiec-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Uruguay ch\u01b0a g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1p s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u0169i c\u00f4ng, nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng. Tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 l\u1ee5c l\u0103ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Fekir, Dembele, Thauvin hay Lemar \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 t\u00e0i v\u00e0 m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi Kante c\u00e0n qu\u00e9t \u1edf ph\u00eda sau, Ph\u00e1p c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i c\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Pogba m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 l\u00e0 c\u00f3 15 l\u00e1 ph\u1ed5i lu\u00f4n thu\u1ed9c t\u1ed1p nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00ecnh tham d\u1ef1. Ch\u00ednh Kante \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n h\u1ed3i sinh Pogba sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u01b0a nh\u01b0 \u00fd t\u1ea1i Man United.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o gu\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 n\u1eefa l\u00e0 Uruguay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 (sau Peru v\u00e0 Argentina).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-thang-tien-tu-ket-world-cup-cong-thuc-chien-thang-mang-ten-pogbappe-421-190444.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/phap-thang-tien-tu-ket-world-cup-cong-thuc-chien-thang-mang-ten-pogbappe.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-thang-tien-tu-ket-world-cup-cong-thuc-chien-thang-mang-ten-pogbappe-421-190444.html\">Ph\u00e1p th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup: C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng mang t\u00ean Pogbappe</span><br>\r\n<span>Kazan, 30 th\u00e1ng S\u00e1u 2018, Ph\u00e1p 4-3 Argentina. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 chia tay World Cup, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00e3i m\u00e3i, \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i cho...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nUruguay thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, Uruguay s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111i t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qu\u00ean nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Luis Suarez v\u00e0 Edinson Cavani.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00e0y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi mang t\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Uruguay. C\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb b\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1ee3c khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Tabarez d\u1eabn d\u1eaft thi\u1ebfu \u0111i Cavani.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cavani chan thuong nghi tran vs Phap\" title=\"Cavani chan thuong nghi tran vs Phap\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Cavani-chan-thuong-nghi-tran-vs-Phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Cavani ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha khi\u1ebfn Cavani kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u0169ng c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Uruguay b\u1edfi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf PSG \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Suarez \u1edf th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Uruguay. Hu\u1ed1ng chi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u World Cup 2018 t\u1edbi nay, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 31 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ed9 r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi sau khi c\u00e0y \u1ea3i c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a c\u00f9ng Barcelona. Chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a La Celeste ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"griezmann va Suarez\" title=\"griezmann va Suarez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/griezmann-va-Suarez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ch\u1ec9 Suarez kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng so \u0111\u1ecd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao Ph\u00e1p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Uruguay. Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean ti\u1ec1n tuy\u1ebfn v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 th\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u HLV Tabarez mong mu\u1ed1n. Song c\u0169ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho Cavani.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu gi\u1eef v\u1eefng 2 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u00ean, Tabarez s\u1ebd c\u00f3 2 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t gi\u00e0, m\u1ed9t tr\u1ebb l\u00e0 Cristhian Stuani v\u00e0 Maxi Gomez. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Stuani (31 tu\u1ed5i) ch\u1ec9 ghi 5 b\u00e0n sau 40 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Uruguay. C\u00f2n Gomez (21 tu\u1ed5i) m\u1edbi c\u00f3 6 tr\u1eadn qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/rami-tho-phao-khi-sat-thu-cavani-chan-thuong-nang-469-190410.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/rami-tho-phao-khi-sat-thu-cavani-chan-thuong-nang.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/rami-tho-phao-khi-sat-thu-cavani-chan-thuong-nang-469-190410.html\">Trung v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p th\u1edf ph\u00e0o khi s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 Cavani ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng</span><br>\r\n<span>Trung v\u1ec7 Adil Rami \u0111\u00e3 th\u1edf ph\u00e0o nh\u1eb9 nh\u00f5m khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cavani d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong 8 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018, ch\u1ec9 Nga (21) l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra \u00edt c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Uruguay (25). Khi v\u1eafng &ldquo;tr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o&rdquo; Cavani, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i th\u1eddi c\u01a1 c\u1ee7a La Celeste c\u00e0ng b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Nizhny Novgorod 21h t\u1ed1i nay (6/7): Uruguay co c\u1ee5m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u1eb1m c\u1ea7u h\u00f2a Ph\u00e1p. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc l\u00f3e s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Les Bleus s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\nUruguay (4-3-2-1):</strong> 1.Muslera - 22.C\u00e1ceres, 2.Gim\u00e9nez, 3.God\u00edn, 17.Laxalt - 8.N\u00e1ndez, 14.Torreira, 15.Vecino - 6.Bentancur, 10.Arrascaeta - 9.Su\u00e1rez<br>\r\n<strong>Ph\u00e1p (4-2-3-1): </strong>1.Lloris - 2.Pavard, 4.Varane, 5.Umtiti, 21.Hern\u00e1ndez - 13.Kant\u00e9, 6.Pogba - 10.Mbapp\u00e9, 7.Griezmann, 18.Fekir - 9.Giroud<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: </strong>Ph\u00e1p th\u1eafng 1-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Uruguay vs Phap\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Uruguay-vs-Phap-(4-3-2-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/antoine-griezmann-phu-phang-voi-diego-godin-421-190167.html\">Antoine Griezmann ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng v\u1edbi Diego Godin</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ldbd-uruguay-xac-nhan-kha-nang-ra-san-cua-cavani-o-tran-gap-dt-phap-421-190362.html\">L\u0110B\u0110 Uruguay c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cavani tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/da-bai-bo-dao-nha-hlv-uruguay-no-tung-bung-469-190071.html\">\u0110\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, HLV Uruguay n\u1ed5 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/matuidi-khang-dinh-mbappe-se-toa-sang-hon-nua-469-190408.html\">Matuidi tin Mbappe s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1eafn h\u1ea1 Uruguay \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/torreira-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-uruguay-vs-phap-421-190425.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"945","checkdouble":"190467"},{"date":"08:42 06/07","title":"R\u1eddi Juventus sang Real Madrid, Ronaldo mang l\u1ed9c cho Man Utd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/roi-juventus-sang-real-madrid-ronaldo-mang-loc-cho-man-utd.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Manchester United v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Sporting Lisbon s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i hoa h\u1ed3ng m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n 2,5% trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus mua Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y: <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-juventus-180-190431.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</span> v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, CR7 s\u1ebd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Bernabeu, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd l\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 kh\u00f3 ai ng\u1edd t\u1edbi cho si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i 2,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro khi Juventus mua Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i 2,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro khi Juventus mua Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/roi-juventus-sang-real-madrid-ronaldo-mang-loc-cho-man-utd.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i 2,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro khi Juventus mua Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real Madrid trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u00e0 Juventus, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p l\u1eafm ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ee7a Paris Saint-Germain hay tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 x\u01b0a Manchester United. \u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Manchester sau bao \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ee9a con c\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb c\u00e1c C\u0110V, ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 vui v\u1ebb v\u00ec nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf \u201ctr\u00ean tr\u1eddi r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, Man Utd s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i hoa h\u1ed3ng m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n 2,5% trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus mua Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real Madrid, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 2,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro hay 2,2 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u1ea3 CLB kh\u1edfi nghi\u1ec7p Sporting Lisbon c\u1ee7a CR7 c\u0169ng h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 1,9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec trong b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2009, Man Utd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u1eb1m h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Real Madrid b\u00e1n Ronaldo trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, nh\u01b0ng lu\u1eadt l\u1ec7 chung v\u1eabn cho ph\u00e9p h\u1ecd c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Sporting Lisbon \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng khi chia tay nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb do ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh Turin nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng ho\u00e0ng, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-juventus-180-190431.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus</span> v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB gi\u00e0u th\u00e0nh t\u00edch nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-dai-dien-vo-tinh-lam-lo-tuong-lai-ronaldo-421-190465.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh l\u00e0m l\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/juventus-coi-nhu-trung-xo-so-neu-chieu-mo-duoc-ronaldo-184-190455.html\">Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo, Serie A coi nh\u01b0 tr\u00fang s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eafc</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain-184-190405.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus s\u1edbm m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 song s\u00e1t t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo - Higuain</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"944","checkdouble":"190468"},{"date":"08:41 06/07","title":"Lukaku: \"Neymar kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/lukaku-neymar-khong-phai-mot-dien-vien.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Romelu Lukaku ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o MU \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i sau nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch nh\u1eafm v\u00e0o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00ec th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede World Cup 2018, Neymar l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t. 4 tr\u1eadn t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i anh b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i t\u1edbi 23 l\u1ea7n, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Romelu Lukaku ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Romelu Lukaku ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/lukaku-neymar-khong-phai-mot-dien-vien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neymar b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch b\u1edfi th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 th\u00f4 thi\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n Neymar tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u201cdi\u1ec5n vi\u00ean\u201d khi l\u0103n l\u1ed9n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi anh l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Mexcio \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, Neymar va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi Miguel Layun b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u00ean.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Layun m\u1edbi ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o Neymar anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u0103n l\u1ed9n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, HLV Juan Carlos Osorio c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Selecao l\u00e0 di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean si\u00eau h\u1ea1ng.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Juan Carlos Osorio sau \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng \u00edt s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh t\u1eeb NHM, h\u1ecd cho r\u1eb1ng Neymar \u00edt di\u1ec5n \u0111i v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lukaku b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c Neymar</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Romelu Lukaku ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o MU \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i sau nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch nh\u1eafm v\u00e0o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00ec th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rat nhieu nguoi chi trich ve viec Neymar an va trong cac tran dau tai World Cup 2018.\" title=\"R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Neymar \u0103n v\u1ea1 trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/thong-ke-day-an-tuong-tai-world-cup-2018-ve-neymar-an-va.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lukaku l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c Neymar</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cAnh \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean. \u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Neymar kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, b\u1edfi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a anh \u1ea5y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cVi\u1ec7c Neymar th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean l\u0103n l\u1ed9n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u, b\u1edfi anh \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, t\u00f4i vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Neymar l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Lukaku, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/dan-anh-bao-ve-thoi-an-va-cua-neymar-421-190406.html\" target=\"_blank\">R\u00f4 b\u00e9o c\u0169ng b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c Neymar</span>, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Brazil c\u00f2n khuy\u00ean c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai, B\u1ec9 vs Brazil trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1ng xem nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup\u00a02018\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"943","checkdouble":"190471"},{"date":"08:57 06/07","title":"HLV Uruguay n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cavani?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/tho-world-cup-tu-ket-bi-braxin.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Oscar Tabarez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Edison Cavani, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 71 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG v\u1eabn b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Oscar Tabarez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cavani</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018, Cavani \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1. Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG \u0111\u00e3 ghi c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap Uruguay \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 2-1 qua \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Oscar Tabarez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Edison Cavani tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Oscar Tabarez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Edison Cavani tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/HLV-Oscar-Tabarez-noi-ve-Edison-Cavani-truoc-tran-gap-Phap-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Uruguay n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cavani\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Uruguay ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n khoeo kh\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng. L\u0110B\u0110 Uruguay x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Oscar Tabarez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Edison Cavani, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 71 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG v\u1eabn b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-phap-21h-ngay-67-thu-manh-co-lai-cong-khung-421-190467.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ph\u00e1p vs Uruguay</span>, t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u1eeb l\u00fac c\u1eadu \u1ea5y d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Uruguay, Cavani \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cavani, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng tin h\u1ecfa m\u00f9 v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 nghi ng\u1edd hay tin \u0111\u1ed3n n\u00e0o\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh Cavani c\u00f3 ra s\u00e2n hay kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0i gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Uruguay \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng C. \u1ede v\u00f2ng 1/8 h\u1ecd xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-3. HLV Oscar Tabarez \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao Les Bleus \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Tabarez\" title=\"HLV Tabarez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/hlv-tabarez-phat-bieu-sau-tran-uruguay-30-nga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Tabarez \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cPh\u00e1p \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi h\u1ecd s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, Ph\u00e1p s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ch\u1ec9 khi l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 Uruguay m\u1edbi c\u00f3 hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Ph\u00e1p r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin v\u00e0o t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"942","checkdouble":"190472"},{"date":"08:51 06/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs B\u1ec9 (01h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7): B\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/6/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-bi-01h00-ngay-77-bua-tiec-tan-cong.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>2 trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nhau v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs B\u1ec9 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2>Brazil v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u00f4ng l\u1edbn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu ai \u0111\u00f3 mong ch\u1edd v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t Selecao ng\u1eabu h\u1ee9ng, b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn nay, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Tite m\u1edbi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, trong \u0111\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t Neymar d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u1eeba qua, Neymar \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ti\u1ebfng vang l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng theo c\u00e1ch ch\u1eb3ng ai mu\u1ed1n khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh &ldquo;k\u1ebb ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n&rdquo; trong m\u1eaft c\u00e1c C\u0110V. M\u1ed9t pha va ch\u1ea1m nh\u1ecf nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y n\u1eb1m l\u0103n l\u1ed9n ra nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 ch\u00e2n b\u1ecb&hellip; \u0111\u1ee9t l\u00eca. N\u00f3i v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng, c\u1ea3 Brazil v\u00e0 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Neymar t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t 100% &ldquo;th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u1ef1c&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, khi lu\u00f4n khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Tite, m\u1ed9t Brazil cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t, nh\u01b0ng ng\u00e2y th\u01a1, \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, nh\u1eefng v\u0169 c\u00f4ng samba ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng con th\u00fa s\u0103n m\u1ed3i &ndash; r\u00ecnh r\u1eadp, ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn, <strong>nh\u01b0ng c\u1ee9 ra tay l\u00e0 ch\u1ebft.</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs B\u1ec9 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs B\u1ec9 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Nhan-dinh-Brazil-vs-Bi-vong-tu-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ch\u01b0a hay nh\u1ea5t, Neymar v\u00e0 Brazil v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng (h\u00f2a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 1-1), Brazil th\u1eafng 3 tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00f3i g\u1ecdn trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi Mexico. Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p, nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00edch m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. 2/4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 85 tr\u1edf \u0111i &ndash; m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f4 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u00e0o \u00e0o nh\u01b0 l\u0169 cu\u1ed1n, Brazil l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i nguy hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch che gi\u1ea5u s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tung ra \u0111\u00f2n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Coutinho v\u00e0 Neymar l\u00e0 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ec9 trong 1 gi\u00e2y, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfn xa, c\u00e0ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea3 4 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m &ldquo;thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed&rdquo; cho Brazil. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9 - \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a World Cup, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Brazil vs Bi la mot trong nhung cap dau tai tu ket World Cup 2018.\" title=\"Brazil vs B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/world-cup-2018-chiec-giay-vang-goi-ten-ai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Brazil vs B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng&rdquo; &ndash; \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ee5m t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9. H\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 4 tr\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua chu\u1ed7i 23 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5y &ndash; \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t so v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0o c\u00f2n s\u00f3t l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. Nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e3y \u0111i v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Roberto Martinez.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca t\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m v\u1eeba qua, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 B\u1ec9 ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111i xa h\u01a1n v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. \u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng l\u1edbn kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Argentina &ndash; h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m c\u1ee7a Brazil. V\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u00f4ng l\u1edbn n\u00e0o (th\u1eafng \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 World Cup, kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u phong \u0111\u1ed9. H\u00e3y n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Kevin De Bruyne &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m hay nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng trong m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba qua, ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u1ede \u0110T B\u1ec9 l\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Eden Hazard &ndash; m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n, d\u00f9 &ldquo;x\u00e1ch d\u00e9p&rdquo; cho Bruyne v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bi 3-0 Panama\" title=\"B\u1ec9 3-0 Panama\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/0.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec9nh cao n\u00e0o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng n\u1ebfu so v\u1edbi \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Brazil. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1edf h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng &ldquo;Bruyne&rdquo; &ndash; nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 100% kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng &ndash; v\u00e0 c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 \u00edt nh\u1eefng &ldquo;Hazard&rdquo;, t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1edbn. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, B\u1ec9 d\u00f9 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a tr\u1ea3i qua b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 b\u00e0i test n\u00e0o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng h\u00fa v\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i 3-2. Nh\u01b0ng h\u00e3y \u0111\u1eb7t ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Brazil trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T B\u1ec9 &ldquo;b\u1eadt l\u1ea1i&rdquo;? Qu\u00e1 \u00edt.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 sao, B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 Brazil ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i khi, kinh nghi\u1ec7m hay b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu thua s\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Selecao, Hazard v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n duy tr\u00ec s\u1ee9c \u00e9p nh\u01b0 Mexico \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf 20 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u &ndash; nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n th\u1ebf, l\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n. B\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng, Brazil s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1eaby, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng kinh nghi\u1ec7m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 B\u1ec9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u0169 m\u00f4n, ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c. C\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd m\u00e3i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 h\u1ed5 gi\u1ea5y.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Brazil vs Bi\" title=\"Preview Brazil vs Bi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Brazil-vs-Bi.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs B\u1ec9 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin b\u00ean l\u1ec1</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Brazil b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 15 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u1ec9 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Brazil th\u1eafng 13/16 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Brazil ghi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn, trong 16/19 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Brazil gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 5/6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 7 l\u1ea7n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, ch\u1ec9 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i 2 l\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Brazil th\u1eafng B\u1ec9 2-0 trong l\u1ea7n duy nh\u1ea5t g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ea1i World Cup 2002, n\u0103m h\u1ecd l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Brazil g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9 5 l\u1ea7n trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, th\u1eafng 3, h\u00f2a 1, thua 1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- B\u1ec9 b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 23 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- B\u1ec9 to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 9 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- B\u1ec9 ghi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn, trong 5/6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Casemiro b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 do nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng, v\u00e0 Fernandinho s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Danilo \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay World Cup v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMarcelo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t theo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Tite. Gabriel Jesus nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi, Firmino \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Kompany \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn th\u00eam 1 th\u1ebb: Philippe Coutinho, Neymar v\u00e0 Filipe Luis (Brazil); Thomas Meunier, Jan&nbsp; Vertonghen, Youri Tielemans, Leander Dendoncker v\u00e0 De Bruyne (B\u1ec9).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Brazil vs Bi\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Brazil vs B\u1ec9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Brazil-vs-Bi-(4-3-3-vs-3-4-3).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Brazil vs B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 Brazil vs B\u1ec9: 2-1</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thong-ke-day-an-tuong-tai-world-cup-2018-ve-neymar-an-va-465-190423.html\">Neymar d\u00e0nh 1/6 th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1eb1m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/kompany-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-bi-vs-brazil-421-190392.html\">Kompany: B\u1ec9 s\u1ee3 g\u00ec c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao Brazil?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-che-duoc-ronaldo-va-messi-ru-ve-nuoc-neymar-mim-cuoi-noi-khong-421-190277.html\">\u1ea2nh ch\u1ebf: \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi r\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc, Neymar m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/neymar-duoc-khuyen-nen-tu-bo-nghiep-cau-thu-va-chon-nghe-dien-vien-421-190281.html\">Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean t\u1eeb b\u1ecf nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn ngh\u1ec1 di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/eden-hazard-thua-nhan-bi-tung-run-so-nhat-ban-465-190236.html\">Eden Hazard th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn B\u1ec9 t\u1eebng run s\u1ee3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/don-quyet-dinh-tieu-diet-samurai-xanh-cua-bi-su-dong-gop-tinh-te-cua-lukaku-421-190257.html\">\u0110\u00f2n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t Samurai xanh c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9: S\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Lukaku</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"941","checkdouble":"190475"},{"date":"19:22 05/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 5/7: L\u00fd do Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-57-ly-do-ronaldo-muon-roi-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 5/7.</h2><h2>T\u1ea1i sao Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real?\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 57 L\u00fd do Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 57 L\u00fd do Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/Moggi-tiet-lo-Ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 5/7: Ronaldo chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Marca kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Cristiano Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid b\u1edfi v\u00ec anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Bernabeu. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid ra gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 anh cho th\u1ea5y CR7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u00e0 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho th\u1ea5y Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juventus t\u1ea1i Serie A.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>PSG \u01b0u ti\u00ean chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kante</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Goal \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng PSG \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kante t\u1eeb Chelsea h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Tanguy Ndombele \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Kante n\u1ebfu m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn theo chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Chelsea c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n Kante. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, PSG c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c g\u00e1n Adrien Rabiot v\u00e0o nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Pavard \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Bayern</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Kicker kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Manchester United v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Benjamin Pavard t\u1eeb Stuttgart. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i 22 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. Pavard \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia nh\u1eadp Bayern nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i \u1edf Stuttgart th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Allianz Arena v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2019.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Bailly ra y\u00eau s\u00e1ch v\u1edbi MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd The Sun cho bi\u1ebft trung v\u1ec7 Eric Bailly mu\u1ed1n th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u1edbi Man United tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford nh\u01b0ng lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Bailly hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Mourinho th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng anh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 15 tr\u1eadn cho MU.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Odriozola ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd AS \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Alvaro Odriozola \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid t\u1eeb Real Sociedad. Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng v\u1ecdt l\u00ean t\u1edbi 40 tri\u1ec7u euro sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 HLV Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n mang \u0111\u1ebfn Real sau khi nh\u1eadm ch\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-0507-mu-va-chelsea-no-bom-tan-cung-luc-184-190395.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 05/07: MU v\u00e0 Chelsea n\u1ed5 &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; c\u00f9ng l\u00fac</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-47-tony-kroos-ra-tuyen-bo-soc-sau-world-cup-2018-421-190377.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 4/7: Toni Kroos s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0a ra tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ed1c sau World Cup 2018?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"940","checkdouble":"190452"},{"date":"20:53 05/07","title":"Ibrahimovic: \"Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd l\u00e0m cho \u0110T Anh ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2m n\u00edn\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/ibrahimovic-thuy-dien-se-lam-cho-dt-anh-phai-cam-nin.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Zlatan Ibrahimovic cho r\u1eb1ng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</h2><h2>Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n Tam S\u01b0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Colombia sau lo\u1ea1t penalty \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 &ldquo;ng\u1ef1a \u00f4&rdquo; Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Zlatan Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u00e0 cho d\u00f9 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n th\u00ec Ibra v\u1eabn kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ibrahimovic\" title=\"Ibrahimovic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/ibrahimovic-thuy-dien-se-lam-cho-dt-anh-phai-cam-nin.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n:&nbsp;Tam S\u01b0 nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1eeb Ibrahimovic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y th\u00ec c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n&ldquo;V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh hay kh\u00f4ng. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac x\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup. \u0110\u1ed9i n\u00e0o ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m x\u00fac t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tuy\u1ec3n Anh. R\u1ed3i sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u00e3y xem David Beckham n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi t\u00f4i n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y&rdquo;.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Ibrahimovic tin Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh, Ibrahimovic c\u00f2n cho r\u1eb1ng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;\u0110\u00fang, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i n\u00f3i khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mexico, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out. V\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n tin v\u00e0o ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft trong n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9. Hy v\u1ecdng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh. V\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ed5 v\u0169 h\u1ecd. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-vong-tu-ket-tam-su-don-nhan-vien-binh-chat-luong-421-190434.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/granqvist-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-thuy-dien-vs-anh-421-190391.html\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"939","checkdouble":"190454"},{"date":"21:19 05/07","title":"Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo, Serie A coi nh\u01b0 tr\u00fang s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eafc","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/juventus-coi-nhu-trung-xo-so-neu-chieu-mo-duoc-ronaldo.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Johan Mjallby cho r\u1eb1ng Emil Forsberg ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Premier League cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 MU, Arsenal hay Liverpool.</h2><h2>Forsberg li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Premier League</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea1i gia Premier League. Trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o RB Leipzig.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Forsberg ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Forsberg ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/Forsberg-chua-du-trinh-da-o-Premier-League-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mjallby cho r\u1eb1ng Emil Forsberg ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nForsberg c\u0169ng\u00a0 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t C\u0110V c\u1ee7a s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i Premier League. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Man United trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> k\u1ebft th\u00fac. B\u1edfi ng\u00f4i sao mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Nga v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<h2>Mjallby ho\u00e0i nghi v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Forsberg</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Johan Mjallby, chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf Premier League l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i h\u01a1i qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Forsberg l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean t\u1edd BetStars tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 Anh, c\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Celtic cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cEmil Forsberg l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111ang d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i Bundesliga. Nh\u01b0ng 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i Anh l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eadp trung nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. S\u1ebd r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t n\u1ebfu Forsberg \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i top 4 Premier League l\u00fac n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T\u00a0Th\u1ee5y\u00a0\u0110i\u1ec3n:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-thuy-dien-se-lam-cho-dt-anh-phai-cam-nin-469-190454.html\">Ibrahimovic: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd l\u00e0m cho \u0110T Anh ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2m n\u00edn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/granqvist-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-thuy-dien-vs-anh-421-190391.html\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"938","checkdouble":"190455"},{"date":"21:36 05/07","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Argentina t\u1ef1 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed v\u00e0o gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng thay Sampaoli","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/huyen-thoai-argentina-tu-ung-cu-vao-ghe-nong-thay-sampaoli.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Mario Kempes kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Argentina n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Jorge Sampaoli b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i.</h2><h2>Sampaoli s\u1eafp b\u1ecb \u201ctr\u1ea3m\u201d</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jorge Sampaoli c\u00f3 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Argentina t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2022. Nh\u01b0ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/jorge-sampaoli-khong-tu-chuc-du-dt-argentina-bi-loai-465-190037.html\" target=\"_blank\">t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Sampaoli</span> \u0111ang r\u1ea5t m\u00f4ng lung khi La Albiceleste ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt l\u00ea b\u01b0\u1edbc qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng mu\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a Rojo tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Sampaoli \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i x\u00e1ch va li v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Ph\u00e1p \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kempes mu\u1ed1n ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng Argentina n\u1ebfu Sampaoli b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kempes mu\u1ed1n ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng Argentina n\u1ebfu Sampaoli b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/huyen-thoai-argentina-tu-ung-cu-vao-ghe-nong-thay-sampaoli.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kempes t\u1ef1 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed thay th\u1ebf Sampaoli</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLi\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Argentina v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 gi\u1eef HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile \u1edf l\u1ea1i hay kh\u00f4ng. Nh\u01b0ng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Kempes mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay th\u1ebf Sampaoli ra m\u1eb7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean k\u00eanh ESPN, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t ch\u00fang c\u1ee7a Argentina th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cTh\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i g\u00e1nh tr\u00ean vai k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Argentina l\u00fac n\u00e0y\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n l\u1eadn \u0111\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Kempes</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Kempes \u0111\u00e3 ghi 2 b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup n\u0103m 1978. \u00d4ng gi\u00e0nh c\u1ea3 danh hi\u1ec7u Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng l\u1eabn Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng World Cup khi Argentina \u0111\u0103ng quang tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Kempes th\u00ec k\u00e9m \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n. \u00d4ng t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Albania, Bolivia v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Indonesia. Nh\u01b0ng trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh n\u1ed5i danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Kempes tham gia c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n l\u00e0 v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2002. \u00d4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ea1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf Italia l\u00e0 Casarano Calcio. Nh\u01b0ng Kempes c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T\u00a0Argentina:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/fifa-ra-toi-hau-thu-cho-maradona-vi-thoi-long-ngon-421-190415.html\">FIFA ra t\u1ed1i h\u1eadu th\u01b0 cho Maradona v\u00ec th\u00f3i l\u1ed9ng ng\u00f4n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/lionel-messi-chia-tay-dt-argentina-hay-nhin-vao-tam-guong-thuy-dien-va-ibrahimovic-466-190357.html\">Lionel Messi chia tay \u0110T Argentina: H\u00e3y nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o t\u1ea5m g\u01b0\u01a1ng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 Ibrahimovic</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"937","checkdouble":"190456"},{"date":"22:18 05/07","title":"Brazil \u0111\u00f3n tin vui t\u1eeb tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/marcelo-tro-lai-tap-luyen-truoc-tran-gap-bi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Tite kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Marcelo \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9 \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</h2><h2>Marcelo b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Real Madrid ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00fang 10 ph\u00fat \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng gi\u1eefa Brazil v\u00e0 Serbia. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/brazil-nhan-tin-du-sau-khi-danh-bai-serbia-469-189804.html\" target=\"_blank\">Marcelo g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span> l\u01b0ng v\u00e0 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ra ngh\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3, Marcelo \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 c\u1ee7a Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, Filipe Luis ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 v\u1eefng ch\u00e3i d\u00f9 Hirving Lozano c\u0169ng \u0111em l\u1ea1i cho anh m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marcelo b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Marcelo b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/marcelo-tro-lai-tap-luyen-truoc-tran-gap-bi.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV\u00a0Tite kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Marcelo b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Tite t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Marcelo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t hay kh\u00f4ng. Nh\u01b0ng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Kazan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cMarcelo v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cFilipe Luis \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Marcelo c\u0169ng \u0111ang d\u1ea7n d\u1ea7n quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Tite ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Jesus thay v\u00ec Firmino</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Roberto Firmino l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Brazil \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Anh ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-0 cho Selecao \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Mexico sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay Jesus. Nh\u01b0ng HLV Tite \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do \u00f4ng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Jesus thay v\u00ec ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cM\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1c nhau \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. S\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p l\u1edbn t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Jesus c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i theo c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u00f4m Firmino v\u00e0 khen c\u1eadu \u1ea5y sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Mexico. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 nghe c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u1ebfu th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn. M\u1ed9t HLV c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T\u00a0Brazil:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ro-beo-neymar-co-the-gianh-qua-bong-vang-2018-421-190440.html\">R\u00f4 b\u00e9o: Neymar c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/bong-da-va-cuoc-phieu-luu-kho-tin-cua-paulinho-389-190453.html\">B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u kh\u00f3 tin c\u1ee7a Paulinho</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"936","checkdouble":"190457"},{"date":"22:36 05/07","title":"Forsberg ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Premier League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/liverpool-va-arsenal-khong-nen-chieu-mo-forsberg.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Johan Mjallby cho r\u1eb1ng Emil Forsberg ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Premier League cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 MU, Arsenal hay Liverpool.</h2><h2>Forsberg li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Premier League</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea1i gia Premier League. Trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o RB Leipzig.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Forsberg ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Forsberg ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/Forsberg-chua-du-trinh-da-o-Premier-League-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mjallby cho r\u1eb1ng Emil Forsberg ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nForsberg c\u0169ng\u00a0 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t C\u0110V c\u1ee7a s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i Premier League. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Man United trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> k\u1ebft th\u00fac. B\u1edfi ng\u00f4i sao mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Nga v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<h2>Mjallby ho\u00e0i nghi v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Forsberg</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Johan Mjallby, chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf Premier League l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i h\u01a1i qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Forsberg l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean t\u1edd BetStars tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 Anh, c\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Celtic cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cEmil Forsberg l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111ang d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i Bundesliga. Nh\u01b0ng 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i Anh l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eadp trung nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. S\u1ebd r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t n\u1ebfu Forsberg \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i top 4 Premier League l\u00fac n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T\u00a0Th\u1ee5y\u00a0\u0110i\u1ec3n:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-thuy-dien-se-lam-cho-dt-anh-phai-cam-nin-469-190454.html\">Ibrahimovic: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd l\u00e0m cho \u0110T Anh ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2m n\u00edn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/granqvist-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-thuy-dien-vs-anh-421-190391.html\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"935","checkdouble":"190458"},{"date":"06:06 06/07","title":"C\u1ef1u th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Wilshere ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf \u1edf CLB Premier League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/18/wilshere-kiem-tra-y-te-tai-west-ham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Wilshere ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i West Ham tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. C\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Arsenal s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c CLB r\u1eb1ng n\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i ph\u00eda sau.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Wilshere chia tay Arsenal</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, Jack Wilshere \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 do. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal sau bu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery. Chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Wilshere s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n b\u1edfi Mesut Ozil t\u1eeb m\u00f9a 2018/19 tr\u1edf \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong kho\u1ea3ng 1 n\u0103m qua, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Ozil c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n t\u00e1n kh\u00f4ng \u00edt. \u0110\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018, anh \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Arsenal l\u00e2u d\u00e0i. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Wilshere, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u00ean mi\u00ean trong th\u1eddi gian qua b\u1ecb h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wilshere ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i West Ham tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Wilshere ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i West Ham tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/18/Wilshere-kiem-tra-y-te-tai-West-Ham-truoc-khi-chuyen-nhuong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Wilshere chia tay Arsenal sau m\u00f9a 2017/18</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nWilshere t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh v\u00e0 ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Arsenal t\u1eeb n\u0103m 16 tu\u1ed5i. Nh\u01b0ng phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f4i khi \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m h\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng n\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfp nhau \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1edd s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u0111ang ch\u1eefng l\u1ea1i tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i West Ham</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong h\u00f4m nay, Wilshere ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i West Ham tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh London v\u1edbi Arsenal \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed5 sung anh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch Premier League 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Wilshere tro lai DT Anh sau nhung man trinh dien tot o CLB\" title=\"Jack Wilshere tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t \u1edf CLB\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/18/wilshere-kiem-tra-y-te-tai-west-ham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Wilshere ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i West Ham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Manuel Pellegrini \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t m\u1ebfn m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Wilshere v\u00e0 th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c West Ham \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Nh\u01b0ng Wilshere tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00ean s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u00e1c b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf chi ti\u1ebft t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh The Hammers.<br>\r\n\u00a0<br>\r\nWest Ham s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1edf kh\u00e2u n\u00e0y v\u00ec mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng Wilshere \u0111ang trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n 39 l\u1ea7n trong 4 m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua t\u1ea1i Premier League cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7, th\u00eam 27 l\u1ea7n cho Bournemouth m\u00f9a 2016/17 d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Jack Wilshere tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/santi-cazorla-co-vai-loi-muon-gui-toi-jack-wilshere-172-189052.html\">Santi Cazorla c\u00f3 v\u00e0i l\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi t\u1edbi Jack Wilshere</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/wilshere-chinh-thuc-roi-arsenal-172-188988.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Wilshere tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eddi Arsenal ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/wilshere-se-chot-tuong-lai-sau-cuoc-gap-hlv-emery-172-188179.html\">Wilshere s\u1ebd ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai sau cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p HLV Emery</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-muon-mua-dennis-praet-cua-sampdoria-172-187155.html\">Arsenal nh\u1eafm sao Serie A thay Wilshere</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"934","checkdouble":"190460"}]}